<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>عن عَونٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>رَوَى عنه مِسْعَرٌ، مُرسلٌ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[٦٧٢٢]</span> عَبْدُ اللَّهِ بْنُ وَهْبَانَ <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>سمعَ ابنَ عبَّاسٍ، قولَه.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>رَوَى عنه عبدُ العَزيزِ بنُ رُفيعٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[٦٧٢٣]</span> عَبْدُ اللَّهِ بْنُ وَدِيعَةَ بْنِ خِدَامٍ <span class="c2">(٣)</span>، الأَنْصَارِيُّ، أَخُو يَزِيدَ بْنِ وَدِيعَةَ، المَدَنِيُّ <span class="c2">(٤)</span> <span class="c2">(٥)</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>سمعَ سَلمانَ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[٦٧٢٤]</span> عَبْدُ اللَّهِ بْنُ وَرْدٍ <span class="c2">(٦)</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>عنْ عامرِ بنِ عبدِ اللَّه بنِ الزُّبيرِ، عن أَبيهِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
